+<html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Preserving Family Knowledge Offline</title><meta name="author" content="Mara Example"><meta property="article:published_time" content="2026-07-01"></head><body><script>window.bad=true;</script><h1>Preserving Family Knowledge Offline</h1><p>A careful archive keeps the original source, a readable copy, attribution metadata, and personal notes as separate layers.</p><h2>Preservation Discipline</h2><p>Hashes help confirm that the original capture has not changed. Deliberate saving prevents accidental collection.</p><h2>Discovery</h2><p>Indexed sections allow grounded questions to cite a capture date, heading, and segment without pretending a web page has PDF page numbers.</p></body></html>
